source.name: FIPS State Codes
source.description: Codes for the identification of the States, the District of Columbia, Puerto Rico, and the Insular Areas of the United States. Contains the 2-digit state FIPS code, postal abbreviation, and 8-digit Geographic Names Information Systems Identifier (GNISID)
